message.content: It is difficult to generalize the interests and obsessions of all kids in Afghanistan, as their preferences can vary greatly depending on factors such as age, location, and socio-economic background. However, like kids in many other parts of the world, Afghan children may be interested in various things such as technology, social media, sports, music, fashion, and entertainment. It is important to remember that children's interests are diverse and can differ from individual to individual.
